<item>
            <title>[LU-19182] dkms build failing with &quot;Error! Build of lustre/lquota/lquota.ko&quot;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19182</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;ins&gt;&lt;b&gt;System Details&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/ins&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;$ uname -r
5.14.0-427.31.1_lustre.el9.x86_64

$ zfs --version
zfs-2.1.15-1

$ cat LUSTRE-VERSION-FILE&#160;
LUSTRE_VERSION = 2.16.1&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;ins&gt;&lt;b&gt;Error Report:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/ins&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;$ rpm &#160;-ivh lustre-zfs-dkms-2.16.1-1.el9.noarch.rpm
...
Error! Build of lustre/lquota/lquota.ko failed for: 5.14.0-427.31.1_lustre.el9.x86_64 (x86_64)
Make sure the name and location of the generated module are correct,
or consult /var/lib/dkms/lustre-zfs/2.16.1/build/make.log for more information.
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;ins&gt;&lt;b&gt;dkms status&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/ins&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;$ dkms status
lustre-zfs/2.16.1: added
zfs/2.1.15, 5.14.0-427.31.1_lustre.el9.x86_64, x86_64: installed (Original modules exist)&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;make.log shows no error. (attached)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
